Client has rhizomes runners coming through their patio and on to the grass lawn
6m x 3m (this area may be extended in size)
Neighbouring property No 10 had a clump of bamboo when the client moved in 3 years ago, which they have since removed and treated possibly a barrier installed.
Client wants a root barrier installed and is aware that distance/ size of this depends when we stop seeing evidence of any growth.They would also like us to quote for a patio to be layed once we have finished installing the barrier and back filling.

Please note access at the widest point through the standard gate is 700mm and narrows to 640 mm.Therefore a hand dig out maybe the only option.
